  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述WorkerNode的生命周期。初始状态应该是Still，然后可以转换到Moving，也可能直接和EtcdCluster交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，WorkerNode作为起始节点指向Still。那Moving和Still之间是双向的吗？还是只能单向流转？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是双向的，Moving可以回到Still。但还有一个关键路径：Moving如果出问题会进入Crash状态，Crash最终要恢复并同步到EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主体结构画出来：WorkerNode启动到Still，Still分出两条线——一条到EtcdCluster做注册，另一条到Moving。Moving回连Still，同时引出Crash。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Still",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，Crash的处理逻辑需要调整。Crash之后不能直接消失，必须重新接入EtcdCluster做状态上报。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我补上了Crash到EtcdCluster的连线。不过Still到EtcdCluster这条线还需要保留吗？还是Crash才是主要的集群通信路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两条线都要保留。Still初始化时注册到EtcdCluster，Crash恢复后也要重新同步。这是两个不同的生命周期阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Crash",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认最终结构：WorkerNode进入Still，Still连接EtcdCluster和Moving；Moving可返回Still或进入Crash；Crash最终连回EtcdCluster完成恢复。这样覆盖所有状态流转了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Still",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
